        <font size='4'><b>GET APRIL FOOLED</b></font><br>
                                <img src='http://graphics.millsberry.com/site_gfx/interiors/gazette/gazette_20090326.jpg' border='1' width='280' height='200'>
                        </div>
        <div id='gazette_byline'><em>By Audrey Smythe-Wei<br>Editor-in-Chief</em></div>
        <b>Thursday, March 26, 2009</b> &mdash;
    People everywhere in Millsberry are getting ready for the craziest holiday of the year: April Fools&#039;. <br><br>It&#039;s hard to know what jokes friends may be planning, but one thing&#039;s for sure: we have some <a href="http://millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=7">excellent goodies</a> to help you with your <a href="http://millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=1">April Fools&#039; mischief</a>. <br><br>Around town, many remember <a href="http://millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=8">April Fools&#039;</a> in the past with some smiles and laughs. <br><br>&quot;There was one year where everyone in town hall rearranged the  <a href="http://millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=3">furniture</a> in my office. That was pretty good,&quot; laughed former Mayor Oliver Trumble. <br>
<br>
&quot;I got them back with a surprise fire drill,&quot; he added smiling. <br><br>Others are a fan of <a href="http://millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=7">April Fools&#039; props</a>.<br><br>&quot;The whoopee cushion is a classic,&quot; exclaimed Coach Danner.<br><br>&quot;I&#039;m also gonna surprise some friends with googly-eyed glasses. But I can&#039;t share my really good April Fools&#039; plans, because I wouldn&#039;t want to ruin the surprise,&quot; Danner added. <br><br>New Mayor Douglas Wright is even planning on making the event an official holiday in Millsberry.<br><br>&quot;I personally think it&#039;s the most fun time of the year. I&#039;ve always been a huge fan of <a href="http://millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=1">April Fools&#039;</a>,&quot; commented Wright.  <br><br>These amazing new items are guaranteed to take your <a href="http://millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=8">April Fools&#039; tricks</a> to the next level. <br><br>Some help with giving your home that funny feeling only the first of April can bring. Others are likely to shock your friends. This promises to be a very entertaining <a href="http://millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=3">April Fools&#039;</a>. <br><br>No matter how you plan to celebrate this April first, the <i>Millsberry <i>Gazette</i></i> wishes you happy fooling!
    </div>

